title: Minecraft But Blocks Randomly Change When You Look At Them
author: Jaavelin
description:
Minecraft But Blocks Randomly Change When You Look At Them
Everywhere you look in minecraft, the block will change to a completely new and random block. Can the best minecraft player in the world (me) find minecraft diamonds with these random blocks spawning over the place, or will I fail like I usually do?
#shorts #minecraft
